<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XnaContent>
  <Asset Type="System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[int,GreenTimeGameData.Components.Chat]">

    <Item>
      <Key>0</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Hi there! How do you like the food?</line>
        </text>
        <showIf>
          <state>
            <name>puzzle_ecologicalstand_solved</name>
            <value>0</value>
          </state>
        </showIf>
        <leadsTo>1</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>1</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>It looks great, but it's too expensive. Outrageous!</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>2 3 4</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>2</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>You're right, the prices are quite high.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>5</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>3</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Still, it is very high quality.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>6</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>4</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>How can you say that right in front of the shopkeeper?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>7</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>
    
    <Item>
      <Key>5</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>I'll get my groceries from somewhere else.</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>6</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>High quality?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>8</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>7</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>It may be rude, but it's true!</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>8</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>This is organic food. It doesn't contain any chemicals or pesticides, and it's harvested with respect for nature and animals.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>9</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>9</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>I still wouldn't buy it.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>10 11 12</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>10</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Do you know how badly the animals in large farms are treated?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>13</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>11</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Have you heard how much genetically modified food is on the market today?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>13</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>12</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Did you know that even babies' milk contains growth hormones?</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>13</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>13</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Is that true? I didn't know that. Maybe you are right...</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>15 14 16</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>14</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>How about I pay half the price for you? Maybe you'll change your mind after you eat some.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>17</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>15</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>The food is healthier and it tastes better, so it's worth the extra money, trust me.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>19</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>16</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Even though it's more expensive, think about nature!</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>18</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>17</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Well, if you're willing to do that for me, I'll try it.</line>
        </text>
        <leadsTo>20</leadsTo>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>18</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Maybe, but I'm still not convinced. We should care for nature, but there are less expensive ways to do that.</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>19</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>I see your point, but I'm still happier with the cheaper food.</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>

    <Item>
      <Key>20</Key>
      <Value>
        <text>
          <line>Thank you! I am sure you will enjoy it.</line>
        </text>
        <affectedStates>
          <state>
            <name>advance_day</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
          <state>
            <name>puzzle_ecologicalstand_solved</name>
            <value>100</value>
          </state>
        </affectedStates>
      </Value>
    </Item>
  </Asset>
</XnaContent>
